        <mxCell id="note_pattern" value="&lt;b&gt;Pattern&lt;/b&gt;: category, subCategory, brand,&lt;br&gt;images, and tags are &lt;b&gt;embedded&lt;/b&gt; in each&lt;br&gt;product document for fast single-read.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Reference collections (categories, brands,&lt;br&gt;tags) are the source of truth for admin&lt;br&gt;CRUD and filter dropdowns.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;On admin update, a sync job denormalizes&lt;br&gt;changes into affected product documents." style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;size=14;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=4;strokeColor=#d6b656;fillColor=#fff2cc;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1">
